{
  "title": "Rich Russian Aubergine Stew",
  "description": "A hearty and flavorful one-pot Russian dish featuring baby aubergine and rest-meat, wrapped in a ti-leaf for added aroma and texture. This jain-friendly stew is perfect for a cold winter's night.",
  "cuisine": "Russian",
